オプション1: Star Man came to the See Poroporo Moss Garden to meet Vim.
The moss garden wasn't very large; with a short walk he could search the whole area.
Vim was pure white and stood out in the forest, so he was easy to find.

Star Man walked over toward Vim.
Vim remained still, staring this way.
"I came to ask about the experimental subject who was with you before—how he's doing."
"Do you know why or how he died?"

"He was killed by a man at a place called Gip Lighthouse."
"When we went there, he was killed."
"I see... That man with the knife."

"I know the man at Gip Lighthouse too.
The moment our eyes met, he tried to kill me with a blade."
"For now, I'll let my companions know."
"We call you Vim. It's the name of a character the children like."
